descriptionHtml:
First thing I want to do is thank princelll for the base model I used to finish my Preset. I also want to thank [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/7656800]H3NT41[/url] for his body preset which gave her life.

This is my closest face model to Hitomi Tanaka so far. As there are so few oriental hair styles to choose from in my collection it was very hard to find something that resembled many of the styles I see her in. I finally put the finishing touches on today. I will be trying various lighting mods to test out and finalize her over time but for the time being for all of her fans here she is. 

Recommended Armor mods to use with her is here: https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29827

Body preset by [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/7656800]H3NT41[/url] can be found here: https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/77062?tab=description

Base files for her face done by princelll can be found here: https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/87340
author: Amarise
